OL,3,CTwo arrested after fire damaged three
OL,4,Ccaravans and supermarket
OL,6,FA man and woman have been arrested
OL,7,Fduring an investigation into a fire in
OL,8,FSomerset that damaged three caravans
OL,9,Fand a supermarket.
OL,11,FThe blaze happened on Beckery New Road
OL,12,Fin Glastonbury at around 8:15pm on
OL,13,FSaturday, 13 June.
OL,15,FThree caravans were damaged, as well
OL,16,Fas the wall of a neighbouring Tesco
OL,17,Fsupermarket, causing the store to be
OL,18,Fevacuated.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
