OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781711308
OL,3,CTwo arrested after fire damaged three
OL,4,Ccaravans and supermarket
OL,6,FTwo people, a man in his forties and a
OL,7,Fwoman in her twenties, were arrested
OL,8,Fon Sunday 14 June, on suspicion of
OL,9,Farson, arson with intent to endanger
OL,10,Flife and assault of an emergency
OL,11,Fworker.
OL,13,FThey have since been released on bail
OL,14,Fwhile officers continue to investigate.
OL,16,FThe force is asking anyone with
OL,17,Finformation to contact them online or
OL,18,Fby calling 101 using the reference
OL,19,Fnumber 5226163150.
